TO DANCE
REPEAT 200 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 200 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 200 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 200 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 200 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
FORWARD 50
RIGHT 80
FORWARD 20
BACK 40
FORWARD 20
BACK 40
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
END

TO FLOWER
SETPENCOLOR 5
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 5 RIGHT 5]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 5 RIGHT 5]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 5 RIGHT 5]
RIGHT 90 
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 5 RIGHT 5]
LEFT 90
SETPENCOLOR 10
FORWARD 200
END

