TO PETAL
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
RIGHT 90 
REPEAT 360 [FORWARD 1 RIGHT 1]
END 

TO PETAL2
