to rectangle :width :height
FORWARD :height
RIGHT 90
FORWARD :width
RIGHT 90
FORWARD :height
RIGHT 90
FORWARD :width
end

TO STAR
SETSCREENCOLOR 17
SETPENCOLOR 6
REPEAT 10 [FD 200 RT 200]
END

